{"tid":1556170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［罷買］中國退回美心月餅","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T15:40:52.000Z","uid":272985,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21c9d63f096d170f20098bdacf2669597cda123e","tid":1556170,"uid":272985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次開po<br />\n就快中秋 想同大家講個小小的正面消息<br />\n<br />\n朋友家人係做美心<br />\n最近從中國退返最少100板月餅<br />\n每板有500盒 每盒4個<br />\n大家可以計下幾多<br />\n<br />\n美心一向賣唔哂就銷毀<br />\n不過呢批貨 <br />\n用高溫風筒熔返張中國標籤出來<br />\n再貼返香港的食品標籤落去<br />\n<br />\n呢個過程係成盒月餅加溫<br />\n膠袋膠盒同裡面的防潮包都一齊㷫埋<br />\n雖然無辦法知道有無事<br />\n但都令人憂心<br />\n<br />\n如果想知自己盒美心月餅係咪中國退回<br />\n（我知大家好齊心罷買，不過可能會被送禮，或者屋企人唔小心買左）<br />\n可以撕走盒底黐到好實的標籤<br />\n如果仲印有日期<br />\n就好大機會係中國退回的貨<br />\n<br />\n請大家注意食品安全，預祝中秋節快樂<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhakXEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvhakXEz.jpg&h=d0b779af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnZqpjA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnZqpjA.jpg&h=99796651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n！"},{"pid":"c34cd8a4e311a5ce860dfbb183a76b6791e088fb","tid":1556170,"uid":112421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"唔買唔食"},{"pid":"2a2499b2daa81df60af584e20db9011f4f1a1598","tid":1556170,"uid":127269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"傳比藍絲知咪冇人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"adb3e8e6f600dc5536cf1e7d1a9b3f6c275567b0","tid":1556170,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"狗也不吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe3ddf67da5593763885c88903180dbbebff2de","tid":1556170,"uid":81333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:37:15.0